name: Buzzy
comments: Parker recorded five takes of "Buzzy" on May 8, 1947 - two of which were incomplete  and all of which have now been released. The fifth take was the original release of the work and appeared on a Savoy 78rpm.  The first take, the original recording,  was released several years later on a Savoy LP.
